(4037, NULL, NULL, 171, 13, 'First of all, I started the day with lunch then I went to shower. \nOnce prepared, I went out to do some shopping.\nAt noon, I cooked for myself and after that I came out to make photocopies and buy envelopes and stamps to finalize my application.\nNaturally, at this moment I candidate by your website, I also earlier in the day prepared some questions about the training that I can ask tomorrow at my appointment at the employment center.\nMore globally, I am interested in Content Management Systems (CMS) and SEO (Search Engine Optimizations).'),
