(4565, NULL, NULL, 193, 13, 'Today i woke up earlier than usual. 13PM ! I like the morning fresh breeze you know. Well, i guess you know that i\'m joking. I woke up at 10AM and did finish the PHP certificate on Sololearn, while listenning to Hayn Piano Sonata, and Stan Getz (i advise you to listen to it, it\'s really beautiful). To be honest i just discovered that it is mandatory for the formation. Since i\'ve learned it (PHP) only on W3Schools i decided to rush the questions. And now, here i am writting my beautiful day (like many others) sitting at home trying to find my way out in this world. Now accept me !\n... Ah... I lack words to end this. Since my day is pretty short in activities i\'ll rather talk about serious business. If Yu-Gi-Oh celebrate christmas eve, will he wear a big Santa\'s hat convering all his spiky hairs, or just one at each spike ? \nAnd did a straw have one hole or two ?\nI bet you know that i can talk english now, congratulation. To be honest my best teacher was my lazyness. Sitting in front of my screen watching series. If you wanna know, i also read books. I tried Descartes \"Le discours de la méthode\", i finished it, but it\'s not easy to read. I\'m actually on \"The Personnal MBA\" of Josh Kaufman, by the way you are using Java for you website and OpenGSE as web server (but we don\'t care), i\'ll read many other books but we can talk about that later. I was impressed to see that you qualify \"Unicorn\" as a gender, you have a sense of humor, i think it\'s a good thing, i did one year in the law highschool at Nice. They miss completely the fact of having fun. Pretty sad isn\'t it ? Today the sky is blue, roses are red and i wish i could do this :\n<?php\necho strlen(\"Hello\");\n?>\nTo count the numbers of characters, (even if it return the length of a string) but you get the point right ?\nOh hey ! Happy new year ! I forgot my manners... I wish you the best (even if it\'s to complete the 300 stuff things to-do... I mean it, it\'s pretty honest ! (I bet nobody dares to says all the stupid things i said here)). To apologize i will leave an imaginary potatoe here. I crossed the limit of 300 words sorry.\n\nYour humble fellow.'),
