(4589, NULL, NULL, 194, 13, 'This morning I woke up with the sunrise. Drinking my coffee, I listen to the radio (most of the time TSF Jazz or France Culture). Then I consult my emails and the news, before e-learning. This very morning I worked on my website : I tried to make some improvement using some CSS and I tried to understand my mistakes. Every day I try to practice and learn with formation online. I think more you try, better it is. Furthermore, I love when I resolve a mistake or when I finish a topic it\'s very satisfying for me ! At the beginning I read a lot but I realize practicing is very important  to understand courses. So now I practice after learning a lesson. I am happy to understand the lessons in English because at the beginning I was a bit afraid of that but it\'s a good way to learn and work and my English is getting better thanks to these lessons.'),
(4590, NULL, NULL, 194, 14, 'Je souhaite intensément me reconvertir professionnellement dans le domaine informatique (qui est un domaine vaste et qui recrute) et cette formation semble en tous points adaptée à ce que je recherche. De plus, il me sera plus facile d\'acquérir des compétences à travers cette formation plutôt qu\'en travaillant en autodidacte de mon côté. Je serais donc très heureuse de pouvoir participer à cette formation de développeuse web.'),
