(4685, NULL, NULL, 198, 13, '\nToday is Saturday,  I start my day  by surfing on my phone ( messenger, facebook, mail….) When an interesting notification make me so exciting : the second session  web developer recrutement is already open at Simplon school. That is an excellent opportunity I’m waiting  for. I believe in my chance. '),
