(4709, NULL, NULL, 199, 13, '  Today, I woke up at 5 o\'clock to go to work at 6 o\'clock. I worked until nine o\'clock and I\'m came back to my house. Arriving, I took a shower  and took a breakfast. After that, I started to take my computeur in order to learn lesson on CodeAcademy. Then I ate a salad, and I went to rest in my bed. '),
(4710, NULL, NULL, 199, 14, '  Selon moi intégrer la formation Developpeur Web est une opportunité de construire mon avenir professionnel. Ce secteur est selon moi, ancré dans la société actuelle et, je pense, va de plus en plus se diversifier.\n  A mon avis, ce métier d\'avenir va se développer et offrir de multiples opportunités dans le futur.'),
(4711, NULL, NULL, 199, 15, 'https://www.codecademy.com/fr/Cinelli_Jeremy'),
(4712, NULL, NULL, 199, 16, 'https://www.sololearn.com/Profile/7958472/PHP'),
