(5549, NULL, NULL, 234, 13, 'Today, I woke up a little late around 10 am. I set up my bed and arranged my room, tidied up the house and cleaned it. I brushed my teeth and took a shower. After the shower, I had lunch, then I checked my emails and I consulted my blog Camertech.com, I responded to the comments left by visitors and I wrote two articles. After all this, at 3 pm I went for a walk to change environment, my friends and I went to the beach where we swam and played football. We met tourists with whom we had a long exchange and then we have returned. I arrived home at 6 pm and took a nap to rest because the beach was tiring. At 8 pm I had dinner with my family, we talked with the family. I went to Facebook where I saw your training, it interested me and I decided to apply. After that it was already late, and it was important for me to go to bed.'),
(5550, NULL, NULL, 234, 14, 'Etant camerounais, Vu que le numérique est l\'avenir.Pour moi je rêve de mettre sur pieds un grand site d\'annonce comme \"Leboncoin\" au cameroun pour faciliter des gens à vendre les outils de second main(occassion) et redonner vie aux outils non utilisés ou négligés (une forme de recyclage en utilisant une plateforme en ligne).\nParce que je constaté que que les camerounais publient des annonces pour vendre des objets dans des groupes Facebook ou whatsapp qui sont des applications web non appropriées pour les ventes en ligne.\nA défaut de cela, je pourrais être enseignant du code et pourquoi pas participer à agrandir la communauté Simplon en ouvrant une filiale au Cameroun.'),
