(6605, NULL, NULL, 278, 13, 'So, this morning, I waked up at 6am and I went to my grandparents to take a lunch. After this good meal, I decided to do a massive study for get in simplon with the help of Sololearn and Code Academy websites. I spent about 4 hours of my precious time to do that :-D.\nI joke, of course, i’m very glad to submit my application for Simplon. '),
