(8093, NULL, NULL, 340, 13, 'Today? it\'s 22:30 am! I m applying for Simplon now because my son is sleeping and I m ZEN :)! So, my sunny Sunday started by  some activities with my Son like his Homework… After this I kept doing something you like !! Guess what?? CODING… in the evening I prepared something to eat.. after my kid have gone to bed, I put those words to your webpage…just for you…'),
